	rking lot\\\, W. McGraw St and 34th Ave W. \\nEnter off W. McGraw St.     
	All Residences and Businesses are invited to bring their important papers 
	\\nto be commercially shredded. Save time and effort while gaining peace o
	f mind that your important papers and information are disposed of in a saf
	e and professional manner.  Old tax records\\\, old files\\\, save time an
	d effort.  A $10 donation per box/bag is suggested.  Donations benefit our
	 501 (c) (3) Rotary Club of Magnolia Charitable Foundation.  We will provi
	de you a tax receipt. First come first served. \\nQuestions\\\, please con
	tact Bryce McWalter\\\, 206-283-2037 or info@magnoliarotary.org.\n\nhttps:
	//discovermagnolia.org/event/just-shred-it-5/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
